Swansea, who have asked about Tottenham's Kyle Naughton, and Sunderland have also shown an interest in Jenkinson.

West Ham are continuing to look for a striker also but strain exists between manager Sam Allardyce and the club's owners.

Hull have also signed Robert Snodgrass, Jake Livermore and Tom Ince this summer.

